data.description: Price change. NEW PICTURES.  4 Bedroom 2 Bathroom home in the heart of John Day.  Laminate, tile, and carpet throughout.  New carpet in 2 Bedrooms.  All appliances included.  Both bathrooms have been updated. New windows and doors inside and out.  Wood stove has been upgraded recently.  Includes separate possible studio apartment all finished except for kitchen area.  Property is comprised of two lots.  Studio is on its own lot.
